Haverty Says Apple Remains `Insanely' Profitable

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-19T00:48:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/haverty-says-apple-remains-insanely-profitable-video-.html
Lawrence Haverty, portfolio manager 
at Gamco Investors Inc., talks about  Apple Inc. (AAPL)  financial 
results and the outlook for the company.  Apple’s profit fell short of analysts’ predictions for 
the first time in at least six years as customers put off 
purchases of iPhones before the release of the latest version. 
Haverty also discusses Yahoo! Inc. He speaks with Susan Li on 
Bloomberg Television's "First Up."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 05:43
 